@Eli Cotham

"Don't Bring Me Down" and "Evil Woman" were in heavy rotation on the local classic rock stations when I was growing up, but I didn't know "Mr. Blue Sky" until it was featured in one of my favorite (Doctor-lite) episodes of Doctor Who. Thanks for the memory!

